Cowboy_Ninja_Viking_Deluxe_Edition_(2013)_(Digital)_(DR_&_Quinch-Empire) 



Collected at last in one giant, oversized, deluxe hardcover are both volumes of the critically acclaimed fan-favorite series COWBOY NINJA VIKING! Featuring all the material in both trades plus brand new, never-before-seen extras! From the author of HARVEST and TERM LIFE and the artist of GREEN WAKE, DIA DE LOS MUERTOS and PROOF! This is one gorgeous volume you'll want to add to your permanent collection! Collects COWBOY NINJA VIKING #1-10.
